  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>While engaged in combat with a creature whom the Land of Bears or the Star Village considers a hostile entity, this adversaries chakra is replaced with a secondary Pool of chakra Equal to [Level * 10], called Star Chakra. <br />Star Chakra can be used to cast Jutsu of any type, and cannot be absorbed or Damaged/reduced by hostile effects. <br />Jutsu cast with Star Chakra cannot be dispelled by hostile effects of a Rank equal to or less than the jutsu Cast.</p>",
